flowchart TD
  A[Google Sheet: HiringCafe search links] --> B[n8n Workflow 01: Ingest Jobs]
  B --> C[jobscraper service (Playwright)]
  C --> D[(n8n Data Table: job_postings)]

  D --> E[n8n Workflow 02: Score Jobs]
  F[(n8n Data Table: prompt_library)] --> E

  E --> G[Ollama (local LLM)\nStructured JSON scoring]
  G --> H[Update job_postings with score + eval]

  H --> I{Score ≥ 20?}
  I -- Yes --> J[Append row to Google Sheet: Application Tracker]
  I -- Yes --> K[Email summary alert]
  I -- No --> L[No alert (kept as scored)]